# Cesium Ion API token. Required for Mars terrain (Cesium Mars asset 3644333)
# and any other catalog terrain block of type "cesium-ion".
#
# Get a token (free Community tier is enough for development):
#   1. Sign up at https://ion.cesium.com/signup/
#   2. Visit https://ion.cesium.com/tokens
#   3. Copy the "Default Token" or create a new one with `assets:read` scope
#   4. Copy this file to .env.local and paste the token below
#
# .env.local is gitignored by Vite — your token won't be committed.
VITE_CESIUM_ION_TOKEN=
